Have you ever dreamed to become a famous CEO ?
Would you like to know what a CEO talks about their life and work ?
Come and attend Apollo_English 360o “ CEO_TALK : FROM_A_TRADER_TO_THE_CEO_OF_HSBC_VIETNAM " by Mr_Hai_Pham_Hong
Date : Tuesday , November 17th , 2015
Time : 6.30pm – 8.00pm
Venue : 4th Floor , Apollo 360 PNT – 58 Pham_Ngoc_Thach , District 3 , Ho_Chi_Minh_City
Seats are subject to availability , follow this link for REGISTRATION : https : / / goo.gl/D1HBJT
Pham_Hong_Hai became the new Chief_Executive_Officer ( CEO ) of HSBC Bank ( Vietnam ) Ltd on 1st December 2014 . He is the first ever Vietnamese person to head operations at this Vietnam ’ s leading foreign - owned bank .
Hai , a well - known and respected figure in the country ’ s banking and finance sector , is also the first ever Vietnamese national to be appointed head of Global_Banking and Markets ( GB& M ) in 2012 . Under his leadership , GB& M developed into one of the largest and most highly - regarded franchises among foreign banks in Vietnam .
Hai personally received a Certificate of Merit for excellence from Trade_Union of the State_Bank of Vietnam for his contribution to the Banking industry of Vietnam between 2011 and 2013
